field_landing_page_summary: VCE is changing from 2023. Victorian senior secondary education is changing. From 2023, the new VCE Vocational Major and Victorian Pathways Certificate will replace VCAL.
field_paragraph_summary: Your senior certificate options are changing. Find out what it means for you.
The VCE is changing to also offer the VCE Vocational Major, a new 2-year program. It will give you work-related skills and prepare you for further education and training.
This new, inclusive certificate will replace Foundation VCAL. The VPC is a flexible program that you can build around your needs.
